{"tid":19830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵小蔡通電話 日本網友：支那人要哭哭了","createTime":"2016-12-03T04:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T07:29:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"665adfdfd10940ec0011eccc5ea6b103748b94b8","tid":19830,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統當選人川普與我國總統蔡英文在電話中大聊台美事務，日本《NHK》報導此事後，日本網友紛紛在社交平台《2ch》討論此事，許多人都調侃，「中國人要哭哭了」。 <br />\n<br />\n川普這通電話有可能影響美中台3國未來關係的走向，在東亞的日本自然很難忽視，《2ch》就湧進大量日本網友發表意見，有人直呼「我愛日本、美國和台灣」，也有人認為這是川普在刻意制衡中國的舉動。 <br />\n<br />\n某位日本網友還笑稱，「新浪（中國網站）現在應該充滿水汪汪的大眼睛」，暗示中國人都在痛哭流涕，還有人高呼川普真的很瘋狂，並猜測他上任後，搞不好會對台灣大規模軍售。"},{"pid":"2bf63590a3f25ad05676ae3a131afb6c3e644fad","tid":19830,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30e1bf1b1d29946f439f2fe733592148cc494ad1","tid":19830,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講英文定國語?</blockquote><br />\n應該係日文<br />\n<br />\n唔係架仔識春睇咩"},{"pid":"752c45de85bd6007df3a7c8d7fc36cc7402338e6","tid":19830,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"台狗又要打飛機了"},{"pid":"62d64f42f4a20ca0556d45d7b81076fc97348bed","tid":19830,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"台灣人要射射了"},{"pid":"4e579ff61cff351c755d898f77328e63a05df982","tid":19830,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:01:06.000Z","msg":"日本人咁抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44060986d1a18176d49b642667d3c3300dc7efc","tid":19830,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}